partnerDetails.about: Edenvale Wholesale's core business is the supply of general and specialised electrical material to many industries. Our large stock holding of products ensures fast and reliable service to customers as well as extremely low competitive pricing. We strive to satisfy all of our customers by ensuring reliable service and by procuring items we do not stock. The business is run by a competent team of staff members who are very service oriented.
